            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Pja7oBNtJTBJZXZUQW2dwL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I don't see any chat history provided in your message. The `<chat-history>` section is empty.\\n\\nTo help you summarize their business idea, I would need you to share:\\n\\n1. **The conversation** between the user and agent about their business idea\\n2. **Any specific details** they've mentioned about:\\n   - What problem they're solving\\n   - Who their target customers are\\n   - What makes their solution unique\\n   - How it works\\n   - Any other relevant context\\n\\nCould you please provide the chat history or the information they've shared about their business idea? Once you do, I'll create a comprehensive summary that captures all the details for your marketing copy.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":117,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":149,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
