            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_016TGFMeggkFUdFC4TxeAB4q\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Audience Summary\\n\\n**Primary Audience: Men in their 50s**\\n\\n- **Age Group:** 50+ years old\\n- **Gender:** Male\\n- **Fitness Level/Background:** Implied to be underserved by existing fitness services\\n- **Key Insight:** This demographic is currently underrepresented in the fitness industry—there's a gap in the market with few trainers/services specifically catering to their needs\\n\\n**Market Opportunity:** The trainer has identified that men in their 50s lack dedicated fitness solutions tailored to their specific needs, goals, and physical considerations, positioning this as a viable niche market.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":287,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":139,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
